snippet.title: Façade trailer
snippet.description:
Trailer for Façade
(c)2007 Procedural Arts, LLC
www.proceduralarts.com

Note that when playing Façade, there are no edits, it is completely real-time and continuous.  

This trailer, however, has many edits, in order to show highlights of the experience.
